targets.expr:
avg (
    sum by (cpu, instance) (
        rate(
            node_cpu_seconds_total{
                mode!="idle",
                databricks_driver="TRUE",
                databricks_cluster_id="$databricks_cluster_id"
            }
            [5m])))

avg (
    sum by (cpu, instance) (
        rate(
            node_cpu_seconds_total{
                mode!="idle",
                databricks_driver="FALSE",
                databricks_cluster_id="$databricks_cluster_id"
            }
            [5m])))

avg by (instance) (
    sum by (cpu, instance) (
        rate(
            node_cpu_seconds_total{
                mode!="idle",
                databricks_driver="FALSE",
                databricks_cluster_id="$databricks_cluster_id"
            }
            [5m])))

rate(
    node_network_receive_bytes_total{
        databricks_driver="FALSE",
        device!="lo",
        databricks_cluster_id="$databricks_cluster_id"}
    [5m]) +
rate(
    node_network_transmit_bytes_total
    [5m])

avg by (instance) (
    sum by (cpu, instance) (
        rate(
            node_cpu_seconds_total{
                mode!="idle",
                databricks_driver="TRUE",
                databricks_cluster_id="$databricks_cluster_id"
            }
            [5m])))

rate(
    node_network_receive_bytes_total{
        databricks_driver="TRUE",
        device!="lo",
        databricks_cluster_id="$databricks_cluster_id"}
    [5m]) +
rate(
    node_network_transmit_bytes_total
    [5m])
